Package gov.nasa.pds.objectAccess.table

Class FloatBinaryFieldAdapter

java.lang.Object
gov.nasa.pds.objectAccess.table.FloatBinaryFieldAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
FieldAdapter
public class FloatBinaryFieldAdapter extends Object implements FieldAdapter
Implements a field adapter for binary, single-precision, floating-point fields.
